n36: | 1.2.3 | Implement `AuthenticationError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n37: | 1.2.4 | Implement `SessionNotFoundError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n38: | 1.2.5 | Implement `ExecutionTimeoutError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n39: | 1.2.6 | Implement `RateLimitError` exception with retry_after | Class defined | 0.25h |\n40: | 1.2.7 | Implement `ValidationError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n41: \n42: **Deliverable:** Complete exception hierarchy.\n43: \n44: ---\n45: \n46: ## ST-1.3 — Data Models\n47: \n48: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n49: |---|------|--------------|------|\n50: | 1.3.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/models.py` | File exists | 0.25h |\n51: | 1.3.2 | Implement `ExecutionResult` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.5h |\n52: | 1.3.3 | Implement `Session` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.5h |\n53: | 1.3.4 | Implement `FileReference` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.25h |\n54: | 1.3.5 | Implement `FileInfo` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.25h |\n55: | 1.3.6 | Implement `Artifact` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.25h |\n56: \n57: **Deliverable:** All data models defined.\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## ST-1.4 — HTTP Client Abstraction\n62: \n63: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n64: |---|------|--------------|------|\n65: | 1.4.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/http_client.py` | File exists | 0.25h |\n66: | 1.4.2 | Implement `HttpClient` protocol/interface | Protocol defined | 0.5h |\n67: | 1.4.3 | Implement `HttpxClient` wrapper class | Wraps httpx.Client | 0.5h |\n68: | 1.4.4 | Add retry configuration with tenacity | Retries on failures | 0.5h |\n69: | 1.4.5 | Implement `AsyncHttpxClient` for async operations | Wraps httpx.AsyncClient | 0.5h |\n70: \n71: **Deliverable:** HTTP client abstraction layer.\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## ST-1.5 — CodeInterpreterClient Core Structure\n76: \n77: | # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n78: |---|------|--------------|------|\n79: | 1.5.1 | Create `python-sd