| pip install -e . works | 0.5h |\n317: \n318: **Deliverable:** All verification checks pass.\n319: \n320: ---\n321: \n322: ## Summary\n323: \n324: | Phase | Tasks | Est. Hours |\n325: |-------|-------|------------|\n326: | ST-1.1: Dependencies | 4 | 1.0h |\n327: | ST-1.2: Exceptions | 7 | 1.75h |\n328: | ST-1.3: Models | 6 | 1.75h |\n329: | ST-1.4: HTTP Client | 5 | 2.25h |\n330: | ST-1.5: Client Core | 5 | 1.5h |\n331: | ST-1.6: Sync Sessions | 5 | 2.25h |\n332: | ST-1.7: Sync Execution | 6 | 2.75h |\n333: | ST-1.8: Sync Files | 5 | 2.5h |\n334: | ST-1.9: Async Structure | 3 | 0.75h |\n335: | ST-1.10: Async Sessions | 3 | 1.5h |\n336: | ST-1.11: Async Execution | 3 | 1.5h |\n337: | ST-1.12: Async Files | 3 | 1.5h |\n338: | ST-1.13: Exports | 5 | 1.25h |\n339: | ST-1.14: Tests — Init | 5 | 2.5h |\n340: | ST-1.15: Tests — Sessions | 6 | 3.0h |\n341: | ST-1.16: Tests — Execution | 7 | 3.5h |\n342: | ST-1.17: Tests — Files | 5 | 2.5h |\n343: | ST-1.18: Tests — Errors | 6 | 3.0h |\n344: | ST-1.19: Tests — Async | 5 | 2.5h |\n345: | ST-1.20: Integration Tests | 4 | 2.0h |\n346: | ST-1.21: Documentation | 5 | 3.0h |\n347: | ST-1.22: Verification | 4 | 1.75h |\n348: | **Total** | **107** | **45.5h** |\n349: \n350: ---\n351: \n352: ## File Deliverables Checklist\n353: \n354: ### Source Files\n355: - [ ] `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter.py` — Client implementation\n356: - [ ] `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/models.py` — Data models\n357: - [ ] `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/exceptions.py` — Custom exceptions\n358: - [ ] `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/http_client.py` — HTTP abstraction\n359: \n360: ### Test Files\n361: - [ ] `python-sdk/tests/test_code_interpreter.py` — Client tests\n362: - [ ] `python-sdk/tests/test_models.py` — Model tests\n363: - [ ] `python-sdk/tests/test_exceptions.py` — Exception tests\n364: \n365: ### Package Files\n366: - [ ] `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/__init__.py` — SDK exports\n367: - [ ] `python-sdk/pyproject.toml` — Dependencies updated\n368: \n369: ---