{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775903312891,"sessionID":"ses_283f1a7caffeQb7fcaz5lxZdpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7c1408480017qR74b1MpAWJZF","messageID":"msg_d7c13f229001gFw7OTcUWZorlC","sessionID":"ses_283f1a7caffeQb7fcaz5lxZdpE","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","content":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n\n> **AR ID:** AR-027\n> **Module:** `sdk-python`\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `CodeInterpreterClient` provides a Python SDK for interacting with the Code Interpreter service, enabling secure sandboxed code execution for AI agents and applications.\n\n---\n\n## ST-3.1 — Project Structure and Dependencies\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 3.1.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/` directory structure | Directory exists | 0.25h |\n| 3.1.2 | Update `python-sdk/pyproject.toml` with httpx dependency | `httpx>=0.25.0` in deps | 0.25h |\n| 3.1.3 | Update `python-sdk/pyproject.toml` with tenacity dependency | `tenacity>=8.0.0` in deps | 0.25h |\n| 3.1.4 | Update `python-sdk/pyproject.toml` with pydantic dependency | `pydantic>=2.0.0` in deps | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** SDK dependencies configured.\n\n---\n\n## ST-3.2 — Exception Hierarchy\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 3.2.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/exceptions.py` | File exists | 0.25h |\n| 3.2.2 | Implement `CodeInterpreterError` base exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n| 3.2.3 | Implement `AuthenticationError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n| 3.2.4 | Implement `SessionNotFoundError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n| 3.2.5 | Implement `ExecutionTimeoutError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n| 3.2.6 | Implement `RateLimitError` exception with retry_after | Class defined | 0.25h |\n| 3.2.7 | Implement `ValidationError` exception | Class defined | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Complete exception hierarchy.\n\n---\n\n## ST-3.3 — Data Models\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 3.3.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/models.py` | File exists | 0.25h |\n| 3.3.2 | Implement `ExecutionResult` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.5h |\n| 3.3.3 | Implement `Session` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.5h |\n| 3.3.4 | Implement `FileReference` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.25h |\n| 3.3.5 | Implement `FileInfo` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.25h |\n| 3.3.6 | Implement `Artifact` Pydantic model | Model validates | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** All data models defined.\n\n---\n\n## ST-3.4 — HTTP Client Abstraction\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 3.4.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/http_client.py` | File exists | 0.25h |\n| 3.4.2 | Implement `HttpClient` protocol/interface | Protocol defined | 0.5h |\n| 3.4.3 | Implement `HttpxClient` wrapper class | Wraps httpx.Client | 0.5h |\n| 3.4.4 | Add retry configuration with tenacity | Retries on failures | 0.5h |\n| 3.4.5 | Implement `AsyncHttpxClient` for async operations | Wraps httpx.AsyncClient | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** HTTP client abstraction layer.\n\n---\n\n## ST-3.5 — CodeInterpreterClient Core Structure\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 3.5.1 | Create `python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/code_interpreter.py` | File exists | 0.25h |\n| 3.5.2 | Implement `CodeInterpreterClient` class definition | Class defined | 0.25h |\n| 3.5.3 | Implement `__init__()` with base_url, api_key, timeout | Parameters stored | 0.5h |\n| 3.5.4 | Add lazy initialization of HTTP client | Client created on first use | 0.25h |\n| 3.5.5 | Add logger initialization | Logger configured | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Core client structure defined.\n\n---\