eptions.py` — Exception tests\n\n### Configuration Files\n- [ ] `python-sdk/pyproject.toml` — Dependencies updated\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 107 tasks complete\n- [ ] Package installs successfully (`pip install -e .`)\n- [ ] Client importable from `agentcube.sdk`\n- [ ] All unit tests pass (>80% coverage)\n- [ ] All integration tests pass\n- [ ] Type checking passes (`mypy`)\n- [ ] Linting passes (`ruff`)\n- [ ] Documentation complete with docstrings\n- [ ] Sync and async APIs working\n- [ ] Session management functional\n- [ ] Code execution working\n- [ ] File operations working\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| `httpx` | >=0.25.0 | HTTP client for API calls |\n| `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | Data validation and models |\n| `tenacity` | >=8.0.0 | Retry logic |\n| `pytest` | >=7.4.0 | Testing framework |\n| `pytest-asyncio` | >=0.21.0 | Async test support |\n| `pytest-cov` | >=4.1.0 | Coverage reporting |\n| `mypy` | >=1.0.0 | Type checking |\n| `ruff` | >=0.1.0 | Linting |\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Install verification\npip install -e \"python-sdk/[dev,test]\"\n\n# Import verification\npython -c \"from agentcube.sdk import CodeInterpreterClient, AsyncCodeInterpreterClient\"\n\n# Unit test verification\npytest python-sdk/tests/test_code_interpreter.py -v\n\n# Coverage report\npytest --cov=agentcube.sdk --cov-report=term-missing\n\n# Type checking\nmypy python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/\n\n# Lint verification\nruff check python-sdk/agentcube/sdk/\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Reference\n\n### CodeInterpreterClient\n\n```python\nfrom agentcube.sdk import CodeInterpreterClient\n\n# Initialize\nclient = CodeInterpreterClient(\n    base_url=\"https://api.agentcube.dev\",\n    api_key=\"your-api-key\",\n    timeout=30.0\n)\n\n# Create session\nsession = client.create_session()\n\n# Execute code\nresult = client.execute_code(\n    code=\"print('Hello World')\",\n    language=\"python\",\n    timeout=10.0\n)\n\n# Upload file\nfile_ref = client.upload_file(session.session_id, \"/path/to/file.py\")\n\n# Close session\nclient.close_session(session.session_id)\n```\n\n### AsyncCodeInterpreterClient\n\n```python\nfrom agentcube.sdk import AsyncCodeInterpreterClient\n\nasync def main():\n    async with AsyncCodeInterpreterClient(\n        base_url=\"https://api.agentcube.dev\",\n        api_key=\"your-api-key\"\n    ) as client:\n        session = await client.create_session()\n        result = await client.execute_code(\"print('Hello')\", language=\"python\")\n        await client.close_session(session.session_id)\n```\n\n---\n\n*AR-027 — Module: sdk-python — Language: Python — Size: M*\n*Stage ST-3: Design Complete — Ready for Implementation*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775903312844,"end":1775903312888}}}}
